videos.description: N.C. State's Abdul-Malik Abu throws down the highlight reel slam.
videos.headline: Abu punishes the rim with a one-handed slam

videos.description: Braxton Beverly hits the 3-ball from the corner to give the Wolfpack the lead.
videos.headline: N.C. State's Beverly gets the triple

videos.description: Clemson runs the fast break to perfection and Donte Grantham finishes with a layup.
videos.headline: Grantham takes the lead in transition

videos.description: Torin Dorn uses a nice spin move and then hangs for the baseline jumper to extend the Wolfpack lead.
videos.headline: Dorn spins for the smooth jumper

videos.description: Torin Dorn gets the steal and finds a wide-open Omer Yurtseven as N.C. State upset No. 19 Clemson.
videos.headline: Yurtseven gets an easy dunk to clinch the upset
